column2: SELECT TOP #  s.legacyPrimary, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subClass, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMagErr_r, p.extinction_r FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE   s.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.petroMag_r < #  AND s.zWarning = #   AND s.class = &&&  AND s.subClass = &&&
